</div>

</figure><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aKIvQ12XIq4" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Watch on YouTube</a></p><p>Currently, there are only two difficulty modes in the game, standard mode - labelled Anvil of the Collective - and a hard mode labelled Forged in Fire ( unlocked after completing the game once on standard mode).</p>
<p>Polish developer Bloober released Cronos back in September and it reviewed well. Our <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/cronos-the-new-dawn-review">Kelsey gave the game four stars in their Cronos: The New Dawn review</a>, calling it "<a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/companies/bloober-team">Bloober Team</a>'s best original game yet". "An immersive romp through a suffocating portrayal of 80s Poland, where your journey is far from what it first seems."</p>
<p>There's currently a Cronos demo available on <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2101960/Cronos_The_New_Dawn/">Steam</a> and <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/cronos-the-new-dawn-85b409">Epic</a>, too, if you fancy giving it a go.</p>

